<subSubSection id="577BC9322AC611B724C9DB02D49B351D" pageId="null" pageNumber="177" type="description">
<paragraph id="9770224ADA8C116944BDA1C8BF9633C6" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
<normalizedToken id="02E72A01439FCA001B4AFE45D3ADF25E" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
3-1 5 mm lang, 
<emphasis id="6F961466FBC6098A275CBC0BC5921494" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">fast ganz frei.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="2CCCF88E9D3C6B5D8866C1CF5FCD8D69" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
im 
<normalizedToken id="97EDFE93B80384B1AB930CD59A4E5F79" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
15-40 mm lang. 
<emphasis id="F8F163D60ACF581E34C97EEDFAB1F802" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Krone 3,5 bis 5 cm im Durchmesser</emphasis>
, nicht punktiert, 
<emphasis id="DE4529A0E1FF65E027743333493CA7E1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
Die 2 untern, 
<normalizedToken id="F2B7E4821064BB310A6D941750054DB2" originalValue="längeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">laengeren</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="335ACD1BF2C5B70421877B78EACD9CC7" originalValue="Staubblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Staubblaetter</normalizedToken>
mit 3
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="7E93E522546CD6FBDE903BC927758CAB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
5,5 mm langen Staubbeuteln. Narbe 
<normalizedToken id="B0A7BDDAD81EC36C5ABF8F8A98136558" originalValue="keulenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">keulenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, am Griffel herablaufend.
</emphasis>
Frucht 5-8 mm lang. Sonst wie 
<taxonomicName id="E5862F4DBE53FDB500F3128C411E8C6B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="177" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="thapsus">
<emphasis id="02B419F27E91084F903016D5BF2DAFDE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">V. Thapsus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr.3a). - 
<normalizedToken id="5F7A1EA4AF309C4E45425D1059402B2D" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3CD1130523FF844A497176DEB58E8BE8" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
<emphasis id="C1A1DAB6018400D27BB05F7BD052EB10" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="5B513800BFCE2EEC48B32583A51568C0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">32:</emphasis>
Material aus Nordeuropa (
<normalizedToken id="B5C218D0BD15C54E8DCC56D3B464780E" originalValue="Håkansson" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Hakansson</normalizedToken>
1926).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F92ADF340DA7A13D71903DD130FCD11A" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
<emphasis id="9F7526A7ABD20847B488E58D28D4CFB3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, selten 
<normalizedToken id="FE1391DD07CC38523B8A488E6F94BD12" originalValue="höher" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">hoeher</normalizedToken>
. Lockere, eher trockene, steinige, 
<normalizedToken id="94613EF03CD3DBA37C6E044269590394" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
, kalkhaltige, lehmige 
<normalizedToken id="4A169A02DDFD3ADD053F695915DF9365" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="0C5D68D2626E93218D17C787E566CF92" originalValue="wärmeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">waermeren</normalizedToken>
Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="A38D13BFB5F8CAC6DD526178F1F732F3" originalValue="Waldschläge" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Waldschlaege</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="2E9463465857DB5668C38BEA30D67CD9" originalValue="Wegränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Wegraender</normalizedToken>
, Kiesgruben, 
<normalizedToken id="6CA022F4C284ABC89607194411489D81" originalValue="Flußgeröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Flussgeroell</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E0915D527EDEC22599395910C6F9CAA8" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
<emphasis id="E52D2E537E19280D3893A13B2FA71CC8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="FC467C30B83C19C7FECA8CFBDCEBD5DC" originalValue="Europäisch-westasiatische" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Europaeisch-westasiatische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="FE2740D816159BD72D22DBB94C30FAB8" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="52087050F4F3DF4A36952070C043383E" originalValue="Südengland" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Suedengland</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="0369F2A1538A7122AC8C404D81032612" originalValue="Südschweden" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Suedschweden</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="5B799A48DC488D9F4CF515867F1AD895" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zum Kaukasus; Marokko (?). - Im Gebiet zerstreut, nicht 
<normalizedToken id="A1017A2C8E9B945150C469BC7AD05C37" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">haeufig</normalizedToken>
(in den Urkantonen nicht vorhanden?); gelegentlich in 
<normalizedToken id="C46B80A0BDC886253129E154D65B247D" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
kultiviert als Zier- und Heilpflanze.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="08E6C6F37972AAE0D8F95F9F2D37B141" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">
<emphasis id="2EB5978638E7F7BD9F2EE1C3A373AD03" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
In der &quot;Flora Europaea&quot; (Vordruck 1970) wird der Name 
<taxonomicName id="3E2CC67ACFC895177667CCACA0FD8F62" authority="Bertol." authorityName="Bertol." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="177" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="densiflorum">
<emphasis id="D5FA9B6747B5ED5E74CE308B56505F01" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">V. densiflorum</emphasis>
Bertol.
</taxonomicName>
verwendet, dessen 
<normalizedToken id="CAA434B0380103BD36E192A0F9178681" originalValue="Identität" pageId="null" pageNumber="177">Identitaet</normalizedToken>
aber nicht sicher ist.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
